    "Overall, the models perform similarly with respect to N, with R 2 of 0.79 ± 0.15 and 0.82 ± 0.03 for ViT and RF, respectively, and for P, with 0.61 ± 0.15 for ViT and 0.58 ± 0.06 for RF, and both models struggle with Mg, a commonly troublesome nutrient for image-based estimation.",
